article.headline: Moody scores 29 to lead Montana to 88-69 victory over Montana State
article.description: — Aanen Moody scored 29 points as Montana beat Montana State 88-69 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Moody scores 29 to lead Montana to 88-69 victory over Montana State
article.story: MISSOULA, Mont. -- — Aanen Moody scored 29 points as Montana beat Montana State 88-69 on Saturday night. Moody was 9-of-17 shooting, including 5 for 9 from 3-point range, and went 6 for 8 from the line for the Grizzlies (17-9, 8-5 Big Sky Conference). Dischon Thomas scored 20 points and added 10 rebounds. Josh Vazquez was 5 of 12 shooting (4 for 9 from 3-point range) to finish with 15 points. The Bobcats (11-15, 6-7) were led by Eddie Turner III with 18 points. Brandon Walker. Robert Ford III also totaled nine points and eight rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
